---
const title = 'How it works – VibeAny';
const description = 'From search to booking in three simple steps. Discover real price drops and book on trusted partners.';
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <style>
      :root { color-scheme: light; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto; }
      body { margin: 0; color: #0f172a; background: #f8fafc; }
      a { color: inherit; }
      header { padding: 40px 24px 48px; text-align: center; }
      nav { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 32px; font-size: 14px; }
      nav a { text-decoration: none; color: #475569; }
      main { max-width: 920px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 24px 80px; }
      h1 { font-size: 40px; margin: 0 0 12px; }
      h2 { margin: 0 0 12px; }
      p { font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; color: #1f2937; }
      .cta { display: inline-block; padding: 12px 20px; border-radius: 999px; background: #2563eb; color: white; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
      .cta.secondary { background: white; color: #2563eb; border: 1px solid #bfdbfe; }
      section { margin: 40px 0; }
      .grid { display: grid; gap: 16px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); }
      .card { background: white; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08); }
      .card p { font-size: 16px; }
      .muted { color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; }
      footer { border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 32px 24px 56px; text-align: center; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/how-it-works">How it works</a>
        <a href="/install-skill">Install skill</a>
      </nav>
      <h1>From search to booking in three simple steps</h1>
      <p>{description}</p>
      <a class="cta" href="#steps">Start searching deals</a>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="steps" class="grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>1. Discover</h2>
          <p>Search by route, destination, or dates. Or browse trending deals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>2. Decide</h2>
          <p>Review price history and provider options to pick the best time.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>3. Book</h2>
          <p>Click through to a partner like Aviasales to complete booking.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Price alerts you control</h2>
        <p>Set a target price or budget. We notify you only when the price actually drops.</p>
        <a class="cta secondary" href="/install-skill">Create an alert</a>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Use it wherever you are</h2>
        <p>Install the skill once and access deal search and alerts from OpenClaw.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Transparency & trust</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card">
            <p>We surface real price drops, not bait.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <p>You always book on the provider’s site (e.g., Aviasales).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <p>No hidden fees added by us.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <p>Prices and availability are subject to change at booking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>FAQ</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>What providers do you check?</h3>
            <p>Major airline, hotel, and aggregator partners (details on the Deals page).</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Do you sell my data?</h3>
            <p>No. You control alerts and can delete them anytime.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>How often do you scan prices?</h3>
            <p>Continuously; alert timing depends on provider updates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>We may earn commissions from partner links (e.g., Aviasales), which helps keep the service running.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
